What:		/sys/devices/platform/exynos-drm/<panel>/power_mode
Date:		June 2024
KernelVersion:	6.1
Contact:	"Attis Chen" <attis@google.com>
Description:
		Userspace client uses this to read the display_on, normal and sleep bits at
		bit 2, 3, 4 respectively of power mode register.

		Valid panels are 'primary-panel' or 'secondary-panel'.

What:		/sys/devices/platform/exynos-drm/<panel>/power_state
Date:		August, 2024
KernelVersion:	6.1
Contact:	"Kevin Ying" <kevinying@google.com>
Description:
		Userspace client uses this to read panel power state. This information
		includes only if the panel is on, off, in low-power mode, or in a HBM state.

		Valid panels are 'primary-panel' or 'secondary-panel'.
